B001C005V001	1	5	1	This is the book of the generations of Adam. In the day that God created man, in the likeness of God made he him;
B001C005V002	1	5	2	Male and female created he them; and blessed them, and called their name Adam, in the day when they were created.
B001C005V003	1	5	3	And Adam lived a hundred and thirty years, and begat a son in his own likeness, after his image; and called his name Seth:
B001C005V004	1	5	4	And the days of Adam after he had begotten Seth were eight hundred years: and he begat sons and daughters:
B001C005V005	1	5	5	And all the days that Adam lived were nine hundred and thirty years: and he died.
B001C005V006	1	5	6	And Seth lived a hundred and five years, and begat Enosh:
B001C005V007	1	5	7	And Seth lived after he begat Enosh eight hundred and seven years, and begat sons and daughters:
B001C005V008	1	5	8	And all the days of Seth were nine hundred and twelve years: and he died.
B001C005V009	1	5	9	And Enosh lived ninety years, and begat Kenan:
B001C005V010	1	5	10	And Enosh lived after he begat Kenan eight hundred and fifteen years, and begat sons and daughters:
B001C005V011	1	5	11	And all the days of Enosh were nine hundred and five years: and he died.
B001C005V012	1	5	12	And Kenan lived seventy years, and begat Mahalalel:
