B001C028V014	1	28	14	
        
B001C028V015	1	28	15	
        
B001C028V016	1	28	16	And Jacob awaked out of his sleep, and he said, Surely the LORD is in this place; and I knew it not.
B001C028V017	1	28	17	And he was afraid, and said, How dreadful is this place! this is none other but the house of God, and this is the gate of heaven.
B001C028V018	1	28	18	And Jacob rose up early in the morning, and took the stone that he had put for his pillows, and set it up for a pillar, and poured oil upon the top of it.
