B001C029V004	1	29	4	And Jacob said unto them, My brethren, from where are you? And they said, Of Haran are we.
B001C029V005	1	29	5	And he said unto them, Do you know Laban the son of Nahor? And they said, We know him.
B001C029V006	1	29	6	And he said unto them, Is he well? And they said, He is well: and, behold, Rachel his daughter comes with the sheep.
