B004C016V007	4	16	7	And put fire in them, and put incense in them before the LORD tomorrow: and it shall be that the man whom the LORD does choose, he shall be holy: you take too much upon you, you sons of Levi.
B004C016V008	4	16	8	And Moses said unto Korah, Hear, I pray you, you sons of Levi:
B004C016V009	4	16	9	Seems it but a small thing unto you, that the God of Israel has separated you from the congregation of Israel, to bring you near to himself to do the service of the tabernacle of the LORD, and to stand before the congregation to minister unto them?
