B004C016V012	4	16	12	And Moses sent to call Dathan and Abiram, the sons of Eliab: who said, We will not come up:
B004C016V013	4	16	13	Is it a small thing that you have brought us up out of a land that flows with milk and honey, to kill us in the wilderness, that you make yourself altogether a prince over us?
B004C016V014	4	16	14	Moreover you have not brought us into a land that flows with milk and honey, or given us inheritance of fields and vineyards: will you put out the eyes of these men? we will not come up.
