B005C002V032	5	2	32	Then Sihon came out against us, he and all his people, to fight at Jahaz.
B005C002V033	5	2	33	And the LORD our God delivered him before us; and we defeated him, and his sons, and all his people.
B005C002V034	5	2	34	And we took all his cities at that time, and utterly destroyed the men, and the women, and the little ones, of every city, we left none to remain:
B005C002V035	5	2	35	Only the cattle we took for a prey unto ourselves, and the spoil of the cities which we took.
B005C002V036	5	2	36	From Aroer, which is by the bank of the river of Arnon, and from the city that is by the river, even unto Gilead, there was not one city too strong for us: the LORD our God delivered all unto us:
