B006C009V015	6	9	15	And Joshua made peace with them, and made a covenant with them, to let them live: and the leaders of the congregation swore to them.
B006C009V016	6	9	16	And it came to pass at the end of three days after they had made a covenant with them, that they heard that they were their neighbors, and that they dwelt among them.
