B007C014V020	7	14	20	But Samson's wife was given to his companion, whom he had used as his best man.
B007C015V001	7	15	1	But it came to pass after a while, in the time of wheat harvest, that Samson visited his wife with a kid; and he said, I will go in to my wife into the chamber. But her father would not allow him to go in.
