B009C014V024	9	14	24	And the men of Israel were distressed that day: for Saul had lain an oath on the people, saying, Cursed be the man that eats any food until evening, that I may be avenged on my enemies. So none of the people tasted any food.
B009C014V025	9	14	25	And all they of the land came to a forest; and there was honey upon the ground.
