B009C018V017	9	18	17	And Saul said to David, Behold my elder daughter Merab, her will I give you as your wife: only be you valiant for me, and fight the LORD'S battles. For Saul said, Let not my hand be upon him, but let the hand of the Philistines be upon him.
B009C018V018	9	18	18	And David said unto Saul, Who am I? and what is my life, or my father's family in Israel, that I should be son-in-law to the king?
