B009C021V009	9	21	9	And the priest said, The sword of Goliath the Philistine, whom you slew in the valley of Elah, behold, it is here wrapped in a cloth behind the ephod: if you will take that, take it: for there is no other except that here. And David said, There is none like that; give it to me.
B009C021V010	9	21	10	And David arose, and fled that day for fear of Saul, and went to Achish the king of Gath.
