B011C004V020	11	4	20	Judah and Israel were many, as the sand which is by the sea in multitude, eating and drinking, and rejoicing.
B011C004V021	11	4	21	And Solomon reigned over all kingdoms from the river unto the land of the Philistines, and unto the border of Egypt: they brought tribute, and served Solomon all the days of his life.
