B011C004V029	11	4	29	And God gave Solomon wisdom and exceedingly great understanding, and largeness of heart, even as the sand that is on the seashore.
B011C004V030	11	4	30	And Solomonâ€™s wisdom excelled the wisdom of all the children of the east country, and all the wisdom of Egypt.
