B011C006V027	11	6	27	And he set the cherubim within the inner house: and they stretched forth the wings of the cherubim, so that the wing of the one touched the one wall, and the wing of the other cherub touched the other wall; and their wings touched one another in the middle of the house.
B011C006V028	11	6	28	And he overlaid the cherubim with gold.
