B011C006V035	11	6	35	And he carved thereon cherubim and palm trees and open flowers: and covered them with gold fitted upon the carved work.
B011C006V036	11	6	36	And he built the inner court with three rows of hewn stone, and a row of cedar beams.
B011C006V037	11	6	37	In the fourth year was the foundation of the house of the LORD laid, in the month Ziv:
B011C006V038	11	6	38	And in the eleventh year, in the month Bul, which is the eighth month, was the house finished throughout all its parts, and according to all its plans. So was he seven years in building it.
B011C007V001	11	7	1	But Solomon was building his own house for thirteen years, and he finished all his house.
