B011C008V023	11	8	23	And he said, LORD God of Israel, there is no God like you, in heaven above, or on earth beneath, who keeps covenant and mercy with your servants that walk before you with all their heart:
B011C008V024	11	8	24	Who has kept with your servant David my father what you promised him: you spoke also with your mouth, and have fulfilled it with your hand, as it is this day.
B011C008V025	11	8	25	Therefore now, LORD God of Israel, keep with your servant David my father that which you promised him, saying, 
