B013C006V016	13	6	16	The sons of Levi; Gershom, Kohath, and Merari.
B013C006V017	13	6	17	And these are the names of the sons of Gershom; Libni, and Shimei.
B013C006V018	13	6	18	And the sons of Kohath were, Amram, and Izhar, and Hebron, and Uzziel.
