B013C006V031	13	6	31	And these are they whom David set over the service of song in the house of the LORD, after the ark had rest.
B013C006V032	13	6	32	And they ministered before the dwelling place of the tabernacle of meeting with singing, until Solomon had built the house of the LORD in Jerusalem: and then they served in their office according to their order.
B013C006V033	13	6	33	And these are they that served with their sons. Of the sons of the Kohathites: Heman the singer, the son of Joel, the son of Samuel,
