B013C006V036	13	6	36	The son of Elkanah, the son of Joel, the son of Azariah, the son of Zephaniah,
B013C006V037	13	6	37	The son of Tahath, the son of Assir, the son of Ebiasaph, the son of Korah,
B013C006V038	13	6	38	The son of Izhar, the son of Kohath, the son of Levi, the son of Israel.
