B013C007V001	13	7	1	Now the sons of Issachar were, Tola, and Puah, Jashub, and Shimron, four.
B013C007V002	13	7	2	And the sons of Tola; Uzzi, and Rephaiah, and Jeriel, and Jahmai, and Ibsam, and Shemuel, heads of their fatherâ€™s house, namely, of Tola: they were valiant men of might in their generations; whose number was in the days of David two and twenty thousand and six hundred.
B013C007V003	13	7	3	And the sons of Uzzi; Izrahiah: and the sons of Izrahiah; Michael and Obadiah, and Joel, Isshiah, five: all of them chief men.
B013C007V004	13	7	4	And with them, by their generations, according to the house of their fathers, were bands of soldiers for war, six and thirty thousand men: for they had many wives and sons.
B013C007V005	13	7	5	And their brethren among all the families of Issachar were valiant men of might, listed in all by their genealogies fourscore and seven thousand.
B013C007V006	13	7	6	The sons of Benjamin: Bela, and Becher, and Jediael, three.
