B013C007V021	13	7	21	And Zabad his son, and Shuthelah his son, and Ezer, and Elead, whom the men of Gath that were born in that land slew, because they came down to take away their cattle.
B013C007V022	13	7	22	And Ephraim their father mourned many days, and his brethren came to comfort him.
