B013C024V008	13	24	8	The third to Harim, the fourth to Seorim,
B013C024V009	13	24	9	The fifth to Malchijah, the sixth to Mijamin,
B013C024V010	13	24	10	The seventh to Hakkoz, the eighth to Abijah,
B013C024V011	13	24	11	The ninth to Jeshuah, the tenth to Shecaniah,
B013C024V012	13	24	12	The eleventh to Eliashib, the twelfth to Jakim,
B013C024V013	13	24	13	The thirteenth to Huppah, the fourteenth to Jeshebeab,
B013C024V014	13	24	14	The fifteenth to Bilgah, the sixteenth to Immer,
B013C024V015	13	24	15	The seventeenth to Hezir, the eighteenth to Happizzez,
B013C024V016	13	24	16	The nineteenth to Pethahiah, the twentieth to Jehezkel,
B013C024V017	13	24	17	The one and twentieth to Jachin, the two and twentieth to Gamul,
B013C024V018	13	24	18	The three and twentieth to Delaiah, the four and twentieth to Maaziah.
B013C024V019	13	24	19	This was the schedule of them in their service to come into the house of the LORD, according to their procedure established under Aaron their father, as the LORD God of Israel had commanded him.
