B013C026V003	13	26	3	Elam the fifth, Jehohanan the sixth, Eliehoenai the seventh.
B013C026V004	13	26	4	Moreover the sons of Obed-edom were, Shemaiah the firstborn, Jehozabad the second, Joah the third, and Sacar the fourth, and Nethanel the fifth,
B013C026V005	13	26	5	Ammiel the sixth, Issachar the seventh, Peullethai the eighth: for God blessed him.
B013C026V006	13	26	6	Also unto Shemaiah his son were sons born, that ruled throughout the house of their father: for they were mighty men of valor.
B013C026V007	13	26	7	The sons of Shemaiah; Othni, and Rephael, and Obed, Elzabad, whose brethren were strong men, Elihu, and Semachiah.
B013C026V008	13	26	8	All these of the sons of Obed-edom: they and their sons and their brethren, able men for strength for the service, were threescore and two of Obed-edom.
B013C026V009	13	26	9	And Meshelemiah had sons and brethren, strong men, eighteen.
