B013C026V011	13	26	11	Hilkiah the second, Tebaliah the third, Zechariah the fourth: all the sons and brethren of Hosah were thirteen.
B013C026V012	13	26	12	Among these were the divisions of the gatekeepers, even among the chief men, having duties like one another, to minister in the house of the LORD.
B013C026V013	13	26	13	And they cast lots, the small as well as the great, according to the house of their fathers, for every gate.
