B013C026V024	13	26	24	And Shebuel the son of Gershom, the son of Moses, was overseer of the treasuries.
B013C026V025	13	26	25	And his brethren by Eliezer; Rehabiah his son, and Jeshaiah his son, and Joram his son, and Zichri his son, and Shelomoth his son.
B013C026V026	13	26	26	This Shelomoth and his brethren were over all the treasuries of the dedicated things, which David the king, and the heads of the fathers' houses, the captains over thousands and hundreds, and the captains of the army, had dedicated.
B013C026V027	13	26	27	Out of the spoils won in battles did they dedicate to maintain the house of the LORD.
