B015C007V001	15	7	1	Now after these things, in the reign of Artaxerxes king of Persia, Ezra the son of Seraiah, the son of Azariah, the son of Hilkiah,
B015C007V002	15	7	2	The son of Shallum, the son of Zadok, the son of Ahitub,
B015C007V003	15	7	3	The son of Amariah, the son of Azariah, the son of Meraioth,
B015C007V004	15	7	4	The son of Zerahiah, the son of Uzzi, the son of Bukki,
B015C007V005	15	7	5	The son of Abishua, the son of Phinehas, the son of Eleazar, the son of Aaron the chief priest:
B015C007V006	15	7	6	This Ezra went up from Babylon; and he was a skilled scribe in the law of Moses, which the LORD God of Israel had given: and the king granted him all his request, according to the hand of the LORD his God upon him.
B015C007V007	15	7	7	And there went up some of the children of Israel, and of the priests, and the Levites, and the singers, and the gatekeepers, and the Nethinim, unto Jerusalem, in the seventh year of Artaxerxes the king.
B015C007V008	15	7	8	And he came to Jerusalem in the fifth month, which was in the seventh year of the king.
