B015C008V004	15	8	4	Of the sons of Pahath-moab; Eliehoenai the son of Zerahiah, and with him two hundred men.
B015C008V005	15	8	5	Of the sons of Shecaniah; the son of Jahaziel, and with him three hundred men.
B015C008V006	15	8	6	Of the sons also of Adin; Ebed the son of Jonathan, and with him fifty men.
B015C008V007	15	8	7	And of the sons of Elam; Jeshaiah the son of Athaliah, and with him seventy men.
B015C008V008	15	8	8	And of the sons of Shephatiah; Zebadiah the son of Michael, and with him fourscore men.
B015C008V009	15	8	9	Of the sons of Joab; Obadiah the son of Jehiel, and with him two hundred and eighteen men.
B015C008V010	15	8	10	And of the sons of Shelomith; the son of Josiphiah, and with him a hundred and threescore men.
B015C008V011	15	8	11	And of the sons of Bebai; Zechariah the son of Bebai, and with him twenty and eight men.
B015C008V012	15	8	12	And of the sons of Azgad; Johanan the son of Hakkatan, and with him a hundred and ten men.
