B016C007V027	16	7	27	The men of Anathoth, a hundred twenty and eight.
B016C007V028	16	7	28	The men of Beth-azmaveth, forty and two.
B016C007V029	16	7	29	The men of Kiriath-jearim, Chephirah, and Beeroth, seven hundred forty and three.
B016C007V030	16	7	30	The men of Ramah and Geba, six hundred twenty and one.
B016C007V031	16	7	31	The men of Michmas, a hundred and twenty and two.
