B016C010V007	16	10	7	Meshullam, Abijah, Mijamin,
B016C010V008	16	10	8	Maaziah, Bilgai, Shemaiah: these were the priests.
B016C010V009	16	10	9	And the Levites: both Jeshua the son of Azaniah, Binnui of the sons of Henadad, Kadmiel;
