B027C005V028	27	5	28	PERES; Your kingdom is divided, and given to the Medes and Persians.
B027C005V029	27	5	29	Then commanded Belshazzar, and they clothed Daniel with scarlet, and put a chain of gold about his neck, and made a proclamation concerning him, that he should be the third ruler in the kingdom.
