B040C002V020	40	2	20	Saying, Arise, and take the young child and his mother, and go into the land of Israel: for they are dead who sought the young child's life.
B040C002V021	40	2	21	And he arose, and took the young child and his mother, and came into the land of Israel.
B040C002V022	40	2	22	But when he heard that Archelaus did reign in Judea in the place of his father Herod, he was afraid to go there: and, being warned of God in a dream, he turned aside into the district of Galilee:
