B044C011V026	44	11	26	And when he had found him, he brought him unto Antioch. And it came to pass, that for a whole year they assembled themselves with the church, and taught many people. And the disciples were called Christians first in Antioch.
B044C011V027	44	11	27	And in these days came prophets from Jerusalem unto Antioch.
B044C011V028	44	11	28	And there stood up one of them named Agabus, and signified by the Spirit that there should be great famine throughout all the world: which came to pass in the days of Claudius Caesar.
