B044C012V001	44	12	1	Now about that time Herod the king stretched forth his hands to persecute certain of the church.
B044C012V002	44	12	2	And he killed James the brother of John with the sword.
B044C012V003	44	12	3	And because he saw it pleased the Jews, he proceeded further to take Peter also. (Then were the days of unleavened bread.)
