B044C022V003	44	22	3	I am verily a man who is a Jew, born in Tarsus, a city in Cilicia, yet brought up in this city at the feet of Gamaliel, and taught according to the perfect manner of the law of the fathers, and was zealous toward God, as you all are this day.
B044C022V004	44	22	4	And I persecuted this way unto the death, binding and delivering into prisons both men and women.
